reviewText: ANOTHER DVD THAT I HAD TO ADD TO MY COLLECTION.  HOPED THAT IT WOULD BE GOOD AND IT TOPPED MY EXPECTATIONS

After watching this presentation, I was really surprised at how little real information about UFOs and the technology associated with it makes it to the public. I am certain this documentary most have covered over a hundred topics related to UFOs and Aliens. I especially enjoyed the information and stories about UFO technology from the Philadelphia Experiment and Montauk Project. The story about the invisible military aircraft that took off in 1966 and time traveled to 1982 really freaked me out! You gotta see this.
Defective disk (not the first one from Bill Knell). Promised refund - never received it. Not recommended.
Secrets Kept And I thought I was the only one with the secret! My UFO was found in South America and the government still has it covered up. Jane
